  From signed offer to first merged PR + first on-call shadow. New hire understands repo layout, runs the dev loop locally, has ship-ready CLAUDE.md/AGENTS.md context, knows incident protocol, and has a named buddy. Output: 30/60/90-day plan filed, first PR merged, retro by day 14.
